8 An Act relating to state government; creating the
Statewide Official Compensation Commission; providing
9 for membership of commission; authorizing meetings
based on meetings of the Board on Legislative
10 Compensation; requiring Statewide Official
Compensation Commission to set salaries for certain
11 public officials; prohibiting modification of salary
amounts in contravention of Section 10 of Article
12 XXIII of the Oklahoma Constitution; amending 74 O.S.
2021, Section 250.4, which relates to state officer
13 salaries; providing for operative effect of salary
provisions; providing for effect of action taken by
14 Statewide Official Compensation Commission; repealing
74 O.S. 2021, Section 250.4, which relates to public
15 official compensation; providing for codification;
